page_title: Azure OpenAI on your Azure Search data Python & REST API reference
page_description: Learn how to use Azure OpenAI on your Azure Search data Python & REST API.
chunk_content: Query typeThe type of Azure Search retrieval query that should be executed when using it as an Azure OpenAI On Your Data.|Enum Value | Description ||---|---||`simple`	|Represents the default, simple query parser.||`semantic`| Represents the semantic query parser for advanced semantic modeling.||`vector`	|Represents vector search over computed data.||`vector_simple_hybrid`	|Represents a combination of the simple query strategy with vector data.||`vector_semantic_hybrid`	|Represents a combination of semantic search and vector data querying.|
